2026-06-04 13:34:32,346 | DEBUG    |   ## Root cause
2026-06-04 13:34:32,346 | DEBUG    |   The `render.AsciiJSON.Render` method incorrectly escapes Unicode code points above U+FFFF (non-BMP characters, such as emojis). The code iterates over runes in the marshaled JSON bytes and, for any rune `r` greater than `unicode.MaxASCII`, attempts to escape it as `\u%04x`.
2026-06-04 13:34:32,346 | DEBUG    |   
2026-06-04 13:34:32,346 | DEBUG    |   However, the `%04x
